once upon a time, in a forest there lived a monkey who resided on a berry tree which was on a banks of the river.In the same forest,there lived a crocdile and his wife.One day, the crocdile 
came to the banks of the river and rested under the tree.So the kind hearted monkey, offered him some fruits.The corcodile came back the next day for more fruits, as he loved them.As days passed by, 
the corcdile and the monkey, became good friends.
